Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:35.59,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}LOVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.93,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}DON'T LET ME DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:38.29,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}LOVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.50,OPED,,0,0,0,,DON'T LET ME DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:45.17,OPED,,0,0,0,,一！二！三！四！五！六！七！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:45.80,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}LOVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.97,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}当心情阴霾　需要阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:52.04,OPED,,0,0,0,,如今是否有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.44,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}能让我去看望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:57.11,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}东边　西边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:59.65,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}何时何地　自由自在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:02.28,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}但现在　所有一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:05.82,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}都落在我肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:09.32,OPED,,0,0,0,,谁都有辛酸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:10.89,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}生活在每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:14.36,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)}LOVE DON'T LET ME DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:15.90,OPED,,0,0,0,,其实不只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:19.40,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)}谁都流过泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:24.01,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}为了告别这样的日子　飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:26.37,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)}ONLY LOVE DON'T LET ME DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:29.31,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}一！二！三！四星球！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:29.98,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}LOVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:33.85,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}DON'T LET ME DOWN
